# RECOLA2-COLLIER PACKAGE README #

* Version 2.2.2

* * *

**Recola2** is a *Fortran95* computer program for the *automated* generation and *numerical* evaluation of amplitudes in *general* quantum field theories at *one-loop* order. It is built on top of [Recola][1] and [Collier][2].

* * *

### External dependencies

+ [CMake][3] build system

* * *

